dct_title_s: Map of the Tennessee River for the use of the Mississippi Squadron
dct_description_sm: Printed at top of title-page: No. 3019, in 17 sheets. Price.; Detailed map of the Tennessee River from Paducah, Ky., to Florence, Ala., showing soundings, distances from Paducah, fortifications, "Wilson's U.S. Cavalry Camp," vegetation, cultivated fields, houses, names of residents, and roads.; See also Civil War Maps entry no. 519.; Description derived from published bibliography.
